{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1460136, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "alice也玩过，宝藏游戏！！！！", "timestamp": 1618481323, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460138, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "真的吗！解谜爱好者狂喜！", "timestamp": 1618481352, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460141, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "高中时候用一个下午通关了！真的很巧妙！就是好短呜呜呜不够玩", "timestamp": 1618481404, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460144, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 会和传统找物、密室类解谜游戏很不一样，可以试试看，游戏流程不长，但需要点耐心来探索玩法（ps 这游戏中文名字叫画中世界，可以先看看宣传片，会节省很多摸索时间）", "timestamp": 1618481464, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460146, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "对的！！！！！！！！永远的神！！！！！！！！", "timestamp": 1618481475, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460147, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "艺术品！！！！", "timestamp": 1618481487, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460165, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "发行商 annapurna 的其他游戏也很精致", "timestamp": 1618481707, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460174, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "确实很不错 不知道lz玩过braid没，觉得不亚于gorogoa的神作", "timestamp": 1618481827, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460188, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可惜现在好多游戏因为没版号，app store都找不到了…这个倒是有steam版本，有的都不知道该去哪儿找正版了", "timestamp": 1618482035, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460208, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 2012, "w": 1080}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是这个嘛？", "timestamp": 1618482269, "type": "image", "url": "pk/pk35icichvqrhlsknlhmyrd3ofubjzus.jpeg"}, {"cid": 1460214, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 是这个！", "timestamp": 1618482287, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460218, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 搜了一下，画风感觉有点古早但设定很有趣的样子，评价也很高，种草了！谢谢推荐！", "timestamp": 1618482316, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460220, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 好的谢谢！这就去装！", "timestamp": 1618482341, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460221, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我也玩过，画面真的太棒了", "timestamp": 1618482341, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460229, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我玩儿过最好的是the room，不过我猜dz肯定也玩儿过了", "timestamp": 1618482432, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460234, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 其实还没有哈哈，不过有看过介绍，也玩过一些同类的。密室类的最近玩得有点多所以想稍微歇一歇，不过之后应该还是会尝试下的", "timestamp": 1618482545, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460441, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这个游戏好好玩的！！而且剧情也很有意思！！", "timestamp": 1618484547, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460734, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "yydd！", "timestamp": 1618488249, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460736, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: yyds(打错了x)", "timestamp": 1618488279, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1460752, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "确实，而且剧情超赞！\n", "timestamp": 1618488523, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1461238, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "无与伦比的解密，天马行空的想象，再搭配上有深度的剧情、恰到好处的音乐和绚丽又朴素的画面。为什么游戏可以说是一种艺术？", "timestamp": 1618493619, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1462071, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "确实好", "timestamp": 1618500481, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1462786, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "确实，刚出的时候就入了，然后沉迷于解密游戏很长一段时间。", "timestamp": 1618505361, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1463127, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不懂就问，这个是手游还是端游啊", "timestamp": 1618530393, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1463207, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Paul", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Olivia: steam上有，也许手机端也有", "timestamp": 1618533173, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1463518, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Queen", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为了刷最后一个成就玩了五次，都快背下来了哈哈", "timestamp": 1618538664, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1464728, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Olivia: 以前手机端是有的（不过说实话在手机上玩有点小），现在反正IOS是没法直接在app store搜到了，sad，还是建议大家steam玩", "timestamp": 1618551537, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1464851, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Richard", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "老番茄之前好像玩过这个！当时就觉得好好玩！！！", "timestamp": 1618553205, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1464876, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Richard: 蛮多游戏up主都做过这个的视频，我看陆夫人玩的", "timestamp": 1618553584, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1465305, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Susan", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "解谜方式很有趣，但也太短了吧？还没动脑子就到ed了？是我错过了什么吗...", "timestamp": 1618558187, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1465356, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Susan", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "写个稍正经点的评价：感谢推荐！\n1. 玩法独特，但谜题简单，一个半小时无攻略通关绰绰有余\n2. 氛围非常到位，bgm棒，画风棒\n3. 比起对各种机关的破解，我觉得思考剧情逻辑才是这个游戏烧脑的谜题，一周目后我对剧情还不能太理解...\n4. 全成就也不简单，一周目只拿了一半成就", "timestamp": 1618558653, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1465753, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Thomas", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "ios有不！", "timestamp": 1618563511, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1465896, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Susan: 洞主本人比较适应短流程的游戏，所以觉得还好，不过steam上的评价中提到的缺点也大部分都说太短了，谜题我自己二周目玩也觉得其实挺简单，不过第一次玩很懵逼的还是浪费了不少时间（说明Susan很厉害！！）剧情方面比较隐晦，不过我看b站实况视频里面大家的讨论，结合自己的理解，我感觉是男孩小时候就找到过一次，然后从楼上摔下来断了腿，后来各个年龄段经历了战争、苦修、战后重建等，老年重新来到塔顶又找回了儿时的那些果实（或者记忆？）", "timestamp": 1618564607, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1466649, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Uma", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我从高中开始就关注这个游戏，直到上了研究生才正式发售", "timestamp": 1618571443, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1466785, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Vivian", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "玩过这个！去年疫情期间在家玩的，还玩了风之旅人", "timestamp": 1618573100, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1467245, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Uma: 五年磨一剑才能有这个质量嘛，而且基本是单人开发的", "timestamp": 1618576988, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1468759, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Susan", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: wow，单人开发太厉害了吧！！", "timestamp": 1618593089, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1476789, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我理解是逆因果律的故事，主角小时候很轻易地找到了，却触发了灾难，原因是他没付出努力，于是穷尽一生付出了很多努力，这些努力倒溯时间线，成为了他小时候找到果实的原因，最终圆满。", "timestamp": 1618722420, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1507664, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 286327, "reply_to": 1460229, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 前段时间把the room的四作都玩完了，谜题说实话不难但机关的精巧简直让我惊叹，光是看着那些柜子盒子打开合上就让我难以自拔了，克系恐怖的氛围做得也不错，除了有时画面实在有点黑之外，别的都很好，感谢推荐", "timestamp": 1619110512, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 1080, "w": 1728}, "likenum": 133, "pid": 286327, "reply": 39, "tag": null, "text": "Gorogoa也太棒了吧，最近沉迷解谜游戏，这绝对是音画最精致、玩法最特别的一个，谜题设计很有挑战性，但找到方法就会变得顺利，充满了天马行空的想象力，最后接近通关的时候被音画震撼到直接落泪。\n强烈推荐给解谜游戏爱好者\n", "timestamp": 1618480998, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1619110513, "url": "5j/5jh2j5fn3kivco22a2f2ni623iyiur4s.jpeg", "vote": {}}}